{"tid":2098080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"7月7日777政府又投放武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-07-07T08:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T09:47:27.000Z","uid":70786,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"20b25c6f00d0665b4fe95734d43ebae244769669","tid":2098080,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港於 1 月 21 日出現首宗輸入的新型冠狀病毒確診個案，患者為武漢人，1 月在 21 日搭高鐵來港，在高鐵西九龍站被發現發燒，即時送院隔離。<span style=\"color: red;\">而同行家人沒有病徵，於 1 月 22 日已轉飛菲律賓馬尼拉。</span></blockquote><br />\n1月唔知放咗幾多病毒走，之後外國大爆發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2670000/2672444/sch170620203_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2670000%2F2672444%2Fsch170620203_1024.jpeg&h=c0fde65a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【源頭】中港跨境兒童、跨境司機和上市國企人員豁免隔離，中國旅客毋須帶隔離手帶<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2097984</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田火炭成重災區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c302c2156371f3c84e4dda2d8c01f52e0d0256","tid":2098080,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"留名睇MON PO狗官出聲明反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f7d718eda1ea178dd10d07d481c8a44f9554fa","tid":2098080,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SqP4GD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SqP4GD.png&h=67b6f744&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"226087d6670d56453390f967cd9c6d91b84e6d59","tid":2098080,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:38:56.000Z","msg":"細思極恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96837ae349743971de979d6f50a0e328e948dd4